flowchart TB
    App([App Server])
    Client[Cache Client<br/>in-process lib<br/>or Twemproxy]
    Node1[(Redis / Memcached<br/>Node 1 RAM)]
    Node2[(Redis / Memcached<br/>Node 2 RAM)]
    NodeN[(Redis / Memcached<br/>Node N RAM)]
    Replica[(Replica<br/>per shard)]
    Sentinel[Redis Sentinel<br/>failover + gossip]

    App -->|get / set| Client
    Client -->|consistent hash| Node1
    Client -->|consistent hash| Node2
    Client -->|consistent hash| NodeN
    Node1 -.->|async repl| Replica
    Sentinel -.->|monitor| Node1
    Sentinel -.->|monitor| Node2
    Sentinel -.->|monitor| NodeN
    Sentinel -.->|promote on failure| Replica

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class App external
    class Client,Sentinel service
    class Node1,Node2,NodeN,Replica store
